<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>index</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background-color: #e8eaed;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 5px;
        }
        .container {
            margin-left: 395px;
            max-width: calc(100% - 435px);
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: #1a1a1a;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .container > h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
        .sidebar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 5px;
            left: 5px;
            width: 365px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            height: 100%;
            overflow-y: auto;
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
        .sidebar a { display: block; padding: 5px 0; color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; }
        .sidebar a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .sidebar ul { list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0; padding-bottom: 20px }
        .sidebar ul li.sidebar-nav-active {
            background-color: #e8ecf1;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .sidebar-filter-wrap {
            margin: 10px 0 12px 0;
        }
        .sidebar-filter-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .sidebar-stat-filter {
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 6px 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .sidebar-stat-filter:focus {
            outline: 2px solid #007BFF;
            outline-offset: 1px;
        }
        h1 { color: #0f172a; font-weight: 700; }
        .check-section-wrapper {
            margin-bottom: 20px; border: 1px solid #007BFF; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px;
            display: flow-root; content-visibility: auto; contain-intrinsic-size: auto 480px;
        }
        .check-section { margin-bottom: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; }
        .check-section h2 { color: #0f172a; margin: 0; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.25rem; }
        .check-section > .file-row {
            display: flow-root;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
            content-visibility: auto; contain-intrinsic-size: auto 320px;
        }
        /* View filters — CSS toggles rows/sections (no per-click walk of every issue row). */
        body[data-mq-view-filter="warning"] .check-section-wrapper[data-mq-section-stat="ERROR"],
        body[data-mq-view-filter="warning"] .sidebar-check-nav[data-mq-sidebar-stat="ERROR"] { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="error"] .check-section-wrapper[data-mq-section-stat="WARNING"],
        body[data-mq-view-filter="error"] .sidebar-check-nav[data-mq-sidebar-stat="WARNING"] { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="flagged"] .file-row:not(:has(.mq-issue-row.flagged)) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="flagged"] .check-section-wrapper:not(:has(.file-row .mq-issue-row.flagged)) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="unflagged"] .file-row:has(.mq-issue-row.flagged) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="unflagged"] .check-section-wrapper:not(:has(.file-row .mq-issue-row:not(.flagged))) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="PRT"] .file-row:not(:has(.mq-issue-row[data-mq-pro-type="PRT"])) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="PRT"] .check-section-wrapper:not(:has(.file-row .mq-issue-row[data-mq-pro-type="PRT"])) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="ASM"] .file-row:not(:has(.mq-issue-row[data-mq-pro-type="ASM"])) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="ASM"] .check-section-wrapper:not(:has(.file-row .mq-issue-row[data-mq-pro-type="ASM"])) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="DRW"] .file-row:not(:has(.mq-issue-row[data-mq-pro-type="DRW"])) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="DRW"] .check-section-wrapper:not(:has(.file-row .mq-issue-row[data-mq-pro-type="DRW"])) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Consistency"] .check-section-wrapper:not([data-mq-category="Consistency"]),
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Consistency"] .sidebar-check-nav:not([data-mq-category="Consistency"]) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Design Intent Strength"] .check-section-wrapper:not([data-mq-category="Design Intent Strength"]),
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Design Intent Strength"] .sidebar-check-nav:not([data-mq-category="Design Intent Strength"]) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Geometry Quality"] .check-section-wrapper:not([data-mq-category="Geometry Quality"]),
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Geometry Quality"] .sidebar-check-nav:not([data-mq-category="Geometry Quality"]) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Model Complexity"] .check-section-wrapper:not([data-mq-category="Model Complexity"]),
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Model Complexity"] .sidebar-check-nav:not([data-mq-category="Model Complexity"]) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Model Integrity"] .check-section-wrapper:not([data-mq-category="Model Integrity"]),
        body[data-mq-view-filter="Model Integrity"] .sidebar-check-nav:not([data-mq-category="Model Integrity"]) { display: none !important; }
        body[data-mq-view-filter="MBD Readiness"] .check-section-wrapper:not([data-mq-category="MBD Readiness"]),
        body[data-mq-view-filter="MBD Readiness"] .sidebar-check-nav:not([data-mq-category="MBD Readiness"]) { display: none !important; }
        .file-list::after {
            content: "";
            display: table;
            clear: both;
        }
        .file-list p { margin: 5px 0; }
        .file-list.mq-bom-scroll-target {
            outline: 2px solid #2563eb;
            outline-offset: 2px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: outline-color 0.4s ease;
        }
        .hide-button { cursor: pointer; background-color: #f0f0f0; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px; padding: 5px 10px; margin-left: 10px; }
        .check-buttons { text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 10px; }
        .file-list .check-buttons { clear: both; }
        .check-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; }
        .check-title { flex-grow: 1; color: #1a1a1a; }
        .summary { background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .bold-text { font-weight: bold; }
        .why img { max-width: 100%; }
        .button {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 4px 2px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .container .button { font-size: inherit; }
        .flagged { background-color: #ffcccc; }
        .file-row:has(.file-list.flagged) > .file-list.flagged { background-color: transparent; }
        .file-row:has(.file-list.flagged) { background-color: #ffcccc; }
        .hidden { display: none; }
        .flag-button { background-color: red; color: white; }
        .dimmed-button { background-color: #e2e8f0; color: #475569; }
        .model-thumb-wrap { float: left; padding: 10px; margin-right: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .model-thumb-wrap img {
            display: block;
            width: 300px;
            height: auto;
            -webkit-user-drag: none;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .model-name-plain { color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: normal; }
        .save-help-overlay {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.45);
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .save-help-overlay.open { display: flex; }
        .save-help-dialog {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 420px;
            width: 100%;
            background: #fff;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 20px 22px 18px;
        }
        .save-help-dialog h2 {
            margin: 0 36px 12px 0;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .save-help-dialog p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            line-height: 1.45;
        }
        .save-help-dialog ol {
            margin: 0 0 14px;
            padding-left: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .save-help-dialog li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .save-help-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 12px;
            right: 12px;
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .save-help-close:hover { background: #e2e8f0; }
        .save-help-actions {
            text-align: right;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .save-help-actions .button { margin: 0; }
        @media print {
            .save-help-overlay { display: none !important; }
            .sidebar, .hide-button, .check-buttons, .print-button, .button { display: none; }
            body { margin: 0; font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a1a1a; }
            .container { margin: 0; max-width: none; box-shadow: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        }
    </style>
    <script defer>
        let hiddenSections = [];
        let scoreViewAdjusted = false;
        let reportSessionDirty = false;
        var mqSummary = null;
        var mqCategoryCards = {};
        var mqPassBaseline = { overall: 0, byCategory: {} };
        var MQ_CATEGORY_FILTER_ORDER = [
            'Consistency',
            'Design Intent Strength',
            'Geometry Quality',
            'Model Complexity',
            'Model Integrity',
            'MBD Readiness'
        ];
        var MQ_MODEL_FILTER_ORDER = ['PRT', 'ASM', 'DRW'];

        function isCategoryFilterMode(mode) {
            return MQ_CATEGORY_FILTER_ORDER.indexOf(mode) !== -1;
        }

        function isModelFilterMode(mode) {
            return MQ_MODEL_FILTER_ORDER.indexOf(mode) !== -1;
        }

        function isSortByIssueCountMode(mode) {
            return mode === 'sort-by-count';
        }

        function mqInitSidebarNavOrder() {
            var navs = document.querySelectorAll('.sidebar-check-nav');
            for (var i = 0; i < navs.length; i++) {
                if (!navs[i].hasAttribute('data-mq-nav-order')) {
                    navs[i].setAttribute('data-mq-nav-order', String(i));
                }
            }
        }

        function mqCountSectionIssues(wrapper) {
            if (!wrapper) { return 0; }
            var rows = wrapper.querySelectorAll('.mq-issue-row');
            var count = 0;
            for (var i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
                var fileRow = fileRowFor(rows[i]);
                if (fileRow && fileRow.parentNode && document.body.contains(fileRow)) {
                    count++;
                }
            }
            return count;
        }

        function mqApplySidebarNavOrder(mode) {
            var ul = document.querySelector('.sidebar ul');
            if (!ul) { return; }
            var hr = ul.querySelector('hr');
            if (!hr) { return; }
            var navs = ul.querySelectorAll('.sidebar-check-nav');
            if (!navs.length) { return; }
            var sorted = [];
            for (var i = 0; i < navs.length; i++) {
                sorted.push(navs[i]);
            }
            if (isSortByIssueCountMode(mode)) {
                sorted.sort(function (a, b) {
                    var wa = document.getElementById(mqNavSectionId(a));
                    var wb = document.getElementById(mqNavSectionId(b));
                    var ca = mqCountSectionIssues(wa);
                    var cb = mqCountSectionIssues(wb);
                    if (cb !== ca) { return cb - ca; }
                    var oa = parseInt(a.getAttribute('data-mq-nav-order') || '0', 10);
                    var ob = parseInt(b.getAttribute('data-mq-nav-order') || '0', 10);
                    return oa - ob;
                });
            } else {
                sorted.sort(function (a, b) {
                    var oa = parseInt(a.getAttribute('data-mq-nav-order') || '0', 10);
                    var ob = parseInt(b.getAttribute('data-mq-nav-order') || '0', 10);
                    return oa - ob;
                });
            }
            var insertAfter = hr;
            for (var j = 0; j < sorted.length; j++) {
                insertAfter.parentNode.insertBefore(sorted[j], insertAfter.nextSibling);
                insertAfter = sorted[j];
            }
        }

        function categoriesPresentInDom() {
            var present = {};
            var sections = document.getElementsByClassName('check-section-wrapper');
            for (var i = 0; i < sections.length; i++) {
                var cat = sections[i].getAttribute('data-mq-category') || '';
                if (cat) { present[cat] = true; }
            }
            return present;
        }

        function syncCategoryFilterOptions() {
            var sel = document.getElementById('sidebar-view-filter');
            if (!sel) { return; }
            var optgroup = document.getElementById('sidebar-category-filter-group');
            if (!optgroup) { return; }

            var present = categoriesPresentInDom();
            var options = optgroup.getElementsByTagName('option');
            for (var j = options.length - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
                var opt = options[j];
                if (!present[opt.value]) {
                    opt.parentNode.removeChild(opt);
                }
            }

            if (!optgroup.getElementsByTagName('option').length && optgroup.parentNode) {
                optgroup.parentNode.removeChild(optgroup);
            }

            if (isCategoryFilterMode(sel.value) && !present[sel.value]) {
                sel.value = 'all';
                document.body.setAttribute('data-mq-view-filter', 'all');
            }
        }

        function proTypesPresentInDom() {
            var present = {};
            var sections = document.getElementsByClassName('check-section-wrapper');
            for (var s = 0; s < sections.length; s++) {
                var rows = sections[s].querySelectorAll('.mq-issue-row[data-mq-pro-type]');
                for (var i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
                    var pro = (rows[i].getAttribute('data-mq-pro-type') || '').toUpperCase();
                    if (pro) { present[pro] = true; }
                }
            }
            return present;
        }

        function syncModelFilterOptions() {
            var sel = document.getElementById('sidebar-view-filter');
            if (!sel) { return; }
            var optgroup = document.getElementById('sidebar-model-filter-group');
            if (!optgroup) { return; }

            var present = proTypesPresentInDom();
            var options = optgroup.getElementsByTagName('option');
            for (var j = options.length - 1; j >= 0; j--) {
                var opt = options[j];
                if (!present[opt.value]) {
                    opt.parentNode.removeChild(opt);
                }
            }

            if (!optgroup.getElementsByTagName('option').length && optgroup.parentNode) {
                optgroup.parentNode.removeChild(optgroup);
            }

            if (isModelFilterMode(sel.value) && !present[sel.value]) {
                sel.value = 'all';
                document.body.setAttribute('data-mq-view-filter', 'all');
            }
        }

        function mqFlaggedFiltersPresentInDom() {
            var flagged = false;
            var unflagged = false;
            var rows = document.querySelectorAll('.mq-issue-row');
            for (var i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
                var fileRow = fileRowFor(rows[i]);
                if (!fileRow || !fileRow.parentNode || !document.body.contains(fileRow)) {
                    continue;
                }
                if (rows[i].classList.contains('flagged')) {
                    flagged = true;
                } else {
                    unflagged = true;
                }
                if (flagged && unflagged) { break; }
            }
            return { flagged: flagged, unflagged: unflagged };
        }

        function mqSetFilterOptionVisible(opt, visible) {
            if (!opt) { return; }
            opt.hidden = !visible;
            opt.disabled = !visible;
        }

        function syncFlaggedFilterOptions() {
            var sel = document.getElementById('sidebar-view-filter');
            if (!sel) { return; }
            var present = mqFlaggedFiltersPresentInDom();
            mqSetFilterOptionVisible(sel.querySelector('option[value="flagged"]'), present.flagged);
            mqSetFilterOptionVisible(sel.querySelector('option[value="unflagged"]'), present.unflagged);
            if ((sel.value === 'flagged' && !present.flagged) ||
                (sel.value === 'unflagged' && !present.unflagged)) {
                sel.value = 'all';
                document.body.removeAttribute('data-mq-view-filter');
                mqSyncSidebarNav();
                mqApplySidebarNavOrder('all');
            }
        }

        function syncViewFilterOptions() {
            syncCategoryFilterOptions();
            syncModelFilterOptions();
            syncFlaggedFilterOptions();
        }

        function openPopup(event, url) {
            const x = event.screenX;
            const y = event.screenY;
            const width = 400;
            const height = 750;
            const left = x - (width / 2);
            const top = y - (height / 2);
            window.open(url, '_named', `width=${width},height=${height},left=${left},top=${top}`);
        }

        function fileRowFor(el) {
            return el && el.closest ? el.closest('.file-row') : null;
        }

        function mqIssueRowFromTarget(el) {
            if (!el) { return null; }
            if (el.classList && el.classList.contains('mq-issue-row')) { return el; }
            return el.querySelector ? el.querySelector('.mq-issue-row') : null;
        }

        function mqNavSectionId(nav) {
            if (!nav) { return ''; }
            var sid = nav.getAttribute('data-mq-section-id');
            if (sid) { return sid; }
            var classes = (nav.className || '').split(/\s+/);
            for (var i = 0; i < classes.length; i++) {
                if (classes[i].indexOf('wrapper-') === 0) { return classes[i]; }
            }
            return '';
        }

        function mqSectionMatchesFilter(wrapper, mode) {
            if (!wrapper || mode === 'all' || isSortByIssueCountMode(mode)) { return true; }
            if (mode === 'warning') { return wrapper.getAttribute('data-mq-section-stat') !== 'ERROR'; }
            if (mode === 'error') { return wrapper.getAttribute('data-mq-section-stat') !== 'WARNING'; }
            if (isCategoryFilterMode(mode)) { return wrapper.getAttribute('data-mq-category') === mode; }
            if (mode === 'flagged') { return wrapper.querySelector('.mq-issue-row.flagged') !== null; }
            if (mode === 'unflagged') { return wrapper.querySelector('.mq-issue-row:not(.flagged)') !== null; }
            if (isModelFilterMode(mode)) {
                return wrapper.querySelector('.mq-issue-row[data-mq-pro-type="' + mode + '"]') !== null;
            }
            return true;
        }

        function mqSyncSidebarNav() {
            var mode = document.body.getAttribute('data-mq-view-filter') || 'all';
            var navs = document.getElementsByClassName('sidebar-check-nav');
            for (var i = 0; i < navs.length; i++) {
                var nav = navs[i];
                var sectionId = mqNavSectionId(nav);
                var wrapper = sectionId ? document.getElementById(sectionId) : null;
                if (!wrapper || !document.body.contains(wrapper)) {
                    nav.style.display = 'none';
                    continue;
                }
                nav.style.display = mqSectionMatchesFilter(wrapper, mode) ? '' : 'none';
            }
        }

        function applyViewFilter() {
            var sel = document.getElementById('sidebar-view-filter');
            if (!sel) { return; }
            var mode = sel.value;
            if (mode === 'all') {
                document.body.removeAttribute('data-mq-view-filter');
            } else {
                document.body.setAttribute('data-mq-view-filter', mode);
            }
            mqSyncSidebarNav();
            mqApplySidebarNavOrder(mode);
        }

        function setViewFilterAll() {
            var sel = document.getElementById('sidebar-view-filter');
            if (sel) { sel.value = 'all'; }
            document.body.removeAttribute('data-mq-view-filter');
            mqSyncSidebarNav();
            mqApplySidebarNavOrder('all');
        }

        function jumpToHealthCheck(checkName) {
            if (!checkName) { return; }
            setViewFilterAll();
            var attr = checkName.replace(/\\/g, '\\\\').replace(/"/g, '\\"');
            var target = document.querySelector('.check-section-wrapper[data-mq-check-name="' + attr + '"][data-mq-section-stat="ERROR"]')
                || document.querySelector('.check-section-wrapper[data-mq-check-name="' + attr + '"]');
            if (!target || !document.body.contains(target)) { return; }
            var heading = target.querySelector('.check-title h2');
            var hash = heading && heading.id ? heading.id : target.id.replace(/^wrapper-/, '');
            if (hash) {
                window.location.hash = hash;
                var sb = document.querySelector('.sidebar');
                if (sb) {
                    var links = sb.querySelectorAll('ul a[href^="#"]');
                    for (var j = 0; j < links.length; j++) {
                        var li = links[j].closest ? links[j].closest('li') : links[j].parentNode;
                        if (li) { li.classList.remove('sidebar-nav-active'); }
                    }
                    var activeLink = sb.querySelector('ul a[href="#' + escapeCssSelector(hash) + '"]');
                    if (activeLink) {
                        var ali = activeLink.closest ? activeLink.closest('li') : activeLink.parentNode;
                        if (ali) { ali.classList.add('sidebar-nav-active'); }
                    }
                }
            }
            target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
        }

        function initHealthCheckJumps() {
            var bars = document.querySelectorAll('.mq-health-jump[data-mq-health-check]');
            for (var i = 0; i < bars.length; i++) {
                bars[i].addEventListener('click', function () {
                    jumpToHealthCheck(this.getAttribute('data-mq-health-check'));
                });
            }
        }

        function jumpToModel(modelName) {
            if (!modelName) { return; }
            setViewFilterAll();
            var needle = modelName.toLowerCase();
            var target = null;
            var rows = document.querySelectorAll('.file-list[data-mq-model]');
            for (var i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
                var m = (rows[i].getAttribute('data-mq-model') || '').toLowerCase();
                if (m === needle) {
                    target = rows[i];
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (!target || !document.body.contains(target)) { return; }
            if (target.id) {
                window.location.hash = target.id;
            }
            target.classList.add('mq-bom-scroll-target');
            setTimeout(function () { target.classList.remove('mq-bom-scroll-target'); }, 2500);
            target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
        }

        function initModelJumps() {
            var btns = document.querySelectorAll('.mq-bom-jump[data-mq-model-jump]');
            for (var i = 0; i < btns.length; i++) {
                btns[i].addEventListener('click', function () {
                    jumpToModel(this.getAttribute('data-mq-model-jump'));
                });
            }
        }

        function mqEmptySummary() {
            return { warnIssues: 0, errIssues: 0, warnModels: {}, errModels: {}, byCategory: {} };
        }

        function mqEnsureCategoryBucket(cat) {
            if (!mqSummary.byCategory[cat]) { mqSummary.byCategory[cat] = { warn: 0, err: 0 }; }
        }

        function mqRowInfo(row) {
            return {
                stat: (row.getAttribute('data-mq-stat') || '').toUpperCase(),
                model: row.getAttribute('data-mq-model') || '',
                category: row.getAttribute('data-mq-category') || ''
            };
        }

        function mqSummaryAddRow(info) {
            if (!info || (info.stat !== 'WARNING' && info.stat !== 'ERROR')) { return; }
            mqEnsureCategoryBucket(info.category);
            if (info.stat === 'WARNING') {
                mqSummary.warnIssues++;
                mqSummary.byCategory[info.category].warn++;
                if (info.model) {
                    mqSummary.warnModels[info.model] = (mqSummary.warnModels[info.model] || 0) + 1;
                }
            } else {
                mqSummary.errIssues++;
                mqSummary.byCategory[info.category].err++;
                if (info.model) {
                    mqSummary.errModels[info.model] = (mqSummary.errModels[info.model] || 0) + 1;
                }
            }
        }

        function mqSummaryRemoveRow(info) {
            if (!info || (info.stat !== 'WARNING' && info.stat !== 'ERROR')) { return; }
            mqEnsureCategoryBucket(info.category);
            if (info.stat === 'WARNING') {
                mqSummary.warnIssues = Math.max(0, mqSummary.warnIssues - 1);
                mqSummary.byCategory[info.category].warn = Math.max(0, mqSummary.byCategory[info.category].warn - 1);
                if (info.model && mqSummary.warnModels[info.model]) {
                    mqSummary.warnModels[info.model]--;
                    if (mqSummary.warnModels[info.model] <= 0) { delete mqSummary.warnModels[info.model]; }
                }
            } else {
                mqSummary.errIssues = Math.max(0, mqSummary.errIssues - 1);
                mqSummary.byCategory[info.category].err = Math.max(0, mqSummary.byCategory[info.category].err - 1);
                if (info.model && mqSummary.errModels[info.model]) {
                    mqSummary.errModels[info.model]--;
                    if (mqSummary.errModels[info.model] <= 0) { delete mqSummary.errModels[info.model]; }
                }
            }
        }

        function mqInitPassBaseline() {
            mqPassBaseline = { overall: 0, byCategory: {} };
            var dash = document.querySelector('.mq-dashboard');
            if (dash) {
                mqPassBaseline.overall = parseInt(dash.getAttribute('data-mq-pass-issues') || '0', 10) || 0;
            }
            var cards = document.querySelectorAll('#mq-categories .mq-cat-card[data-mq-category]');
            for (var i = 0; i < cards.length; i++) {
                var card = cards[i];
                var catName = card.getAttribute('data-mq-category') || '';
                mqPassBaseline.byCategory[catName] = parseInt(card.getAttribute('data-mq-pass') || '0', 10) || 0;
            }
        }

        function mqInitCategoryCards() {
            mqCategoryCards = {};
            var cards = document.querySelectorAll('#mq-categories .mq-cat-card[data-mq-category]');
            for (var c = 0; c < cards.length; c++) {
                var card = cards[c];
                var catName = card.getAttribute('data-mq-category') || '';
                mqCategoryCards[catName] = {
                    card: card,
                    badge: card.querySelector('[data-mq-role="badge"]'),
                    segWarn: card.querySelector('[data-mq-role="seg-warn"]'),
                    segErr: card.querySelector('[data-mq-role="seg-err"]'),
                    segPass: card.querySelector('[data-mq-role="seg-pass"]'),
                    stack: card.querySelector('[data-mq-role="stack"]'),
                    warnCount: card.querySelector('[data-mq-role="warn-count"]'),
                    errCount: card.querySelector('[data-mq-role="err-count"]')
                };
            }
        }

        function mqRebuildSummaryFromDom() {
            mqSummary = mqEmptySummary();
            var rows = document.querySelectorAll('.mq-issue-row');
            for (var i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
                mqSummaryAddRow(mqRowInfo(rows[i]));
            }
        }

        function mqEnsureSummary() {
            if (mqSummary) { return; }
            mqRebuildSummaryFromDom();
        }

        function mqApplySummaryToDom() {
            mqEnsureSummary();
            var warnIssues = mqSummary.warnIssues;
            var errIssues = mqSummary.errIssues;
            var issuesEl = document.getElementById('mq-stat-issues');
            var warnModelsEl = document.getElementById('mq-stat-warn-models');
            var errModelsEl = document.getElementById('mq-stat-err-models');
            if (issuesEl) { issuesEl.textContent = String(warnIssues + errIssues); }
            if (warnModelsEl) { warnModelsEl.textContent = String(Object.keys(mqSummary.warnModels).length); }
            if (errModelsEl) { errModelsEl.textContent = String(Object.keys(mqSummary.errModels).length); }
            mqSetGradeRing(
                document.getElementById('mq-overall-grade'),
                mqGradeFromCounts(mqPassBaseline.overall, warnIssues, errIssues)
            );
            var titleEl = document.getElementById('mq-page-title');
            if (titleEl) {
                titleEl.textContent = scoreViewAdjusted ? 'Adjusted Score' : 'Score';
            }
            for (var catName in mqCategoryCards) {
                if (!mqCategoryCards.hasOwnProperty(catName)) { continue; }
                var refs = mqCategoryCards[catName];
                var counts = mqSummary.byCategory[catName] || { warn: 0, err: 0 };
                var w = counts.warn;
                var e = counts.err;
                var pass = mqPassBaseline.byCategory[catName] || 0;
                refs.card.classList.remove('mq-cat-empty');
                var letter = mqGradeFromCounts(pass, w, e);
                var total = pass + w + e;
                var gPct = total ? (pass / total) * 100 : 0;
                var yPct = total ? (w / total) * 100 : 0;
                var rPct = total ? (e / total) * 100 : 0;
                mqSetCategoryBadge(refs.badge, letter);
                if (refs.segPass) { refs.segPass.style.width = gPct.toFixed(4) + '%'; }
                if (refs.segWarn) { refs.segWarn.style.width = yPct.toFixed(4) + '%'; }
                if (refs.segErr) { refs.segErr.style.width = rPct.toFixed(4) + '%'; }
                if (refs.stack) {
                    refs.stack.title = gPct.toFixed(2) + '% pass, ' + yPct.toFixed(2) + '% warning, ' + rPct.toFixed(2) + '% error';
                }
                if (refs.warnCount) { refs.warnCount.textContent = String(w); }
                if (refs.errCount) { refs.errCount.textContent = String(e); }
            }
            updateSaveButtonVisibility();
        }

        function markReportSessionDirty() {
            reportSessionDirty = true;
        }

        function clearReportSessionDirty() {
            reportSessionDirty = false;
        }

        function mqOnReportMutation(opts) {
            opts = opts || {};
            scoreViewAdjusted = true;
            markReportSessionDirty();
            if (opts.syncFilters) { syncViewFilterOptions(); }
            mqApplySummaryToDom();
            if (opts.syncNav) {
                mqSyncSidebarNav();
                mqApplySidebarNavOrder(document.body.getAttribute('data-mq-view-filter') || 'all');
            }
        }

        function toggleFlag(id) {
            var element = document.getElementById(id);
            if (!element) { return; }
            var flagButton = element.querySelector('.flag-button');
            element.classList.toggle('flagged');
            if (flagButton) { flagButton.classList.toggle('dimmed-button'); }
            syncFlaggedFilterOptions();
            var mode = document.body.getAttribute('data-mq-view-filter') || 'all';
            if (mode === 'flagged' || mode === 'unflagged') { mqSyncSidebarNav(); }
            markReportSessionDirty();
            updateSaveButtonVisibility();
        }

        function escapeCssSelector(selector) {
            return selector.replace(/([\:\.\[\],=|@!"#$%&'()*+;<>?\\^`{}~])/g, "\\$1");
        }

        function mqGradeClass(letter) {
            var map = { A: 'mq-grade-a', B: 'mq-grade-b', C: 'mq-grade-c', D: 'mq-grade-d' };
            return map[letter] || 'mq-grade-na';
        }

        function mqGradeFromCounts(pass, warn, err) {
            var total = pass + warn + err;
            if (total === 0) { return 'A'; }
            if (err > 0) { return 'D'; }
            var yellowRatio = warn / total;
            if (yellowRatio > 0.25) { return 'C'; }
            if (yellowRatio >= 0.05) { return 'B'; }
            return 'A';
        }

        function mqSetGradeRing(el, letter) {
            if (!el) { return; }
            el.textContent = letter;
            el.className = 'mq-grade-ring ' + mqGradeClass(letter);
        }

        function mqSetCategoryBadge(badge, letter) {
            if (!badge) { return; }
            badge.textContent = letter;
            badge.className = 'mq-cat-badge ' + mqGradeClass(letter);
        }

        function recalculateAdjustedSummary() {
            mqRebuildSummaryFromDom();
            mqApplySummaryToDom();
        }

        function reportHasUnsavedChanges() {
            if (scoreViewAdjusted) { return true; }
            return document.querySelector('.file-list.flagged') !== null;
        }

        function updateSaveButtonVisibility() {
            var btn = document.getElementById('save-help-button');
            if (btn) {
                btn.style.display = reportHasUnsavedChanges() ? '' : 'none';
            }
        }

        function hideElementById(id) {
            var element = document.getElementById(id);
            if (element) {
                var issueRow = mqIssueRowFromTarget(element);
                if (issueRow) {
                    mqEnsureSummary();
                    mqSummaryRemoveRow(mqRowInfo(issueRow));
                }
                var toRemove = fileRowFor(element) || element;
                toRemove.parentNode.removeChild(toRemove);
                var escapedId = escapeCssSelector(id);
                var sidebarItem = document.querySelector('.sidebar .' + escapedId);
                if (sidebarItem) { sidebarItem.parentNode.removeChild(sidebarItem); }
                hiddenSections = hiddenSections.filter(sec => sec !== id);
            }
            removeEmptyCheckSections();
            mqOnReportMutation({ syncFilters: true, syncNav: true });
        }

        function hideElementsByClass(className) {
            var escapedClass = escapeCssSelector(className);
            var elements = document.getElementsByClassName(escapedClass);
            mqEnsureSummary();
            var toRemove = [];
            for (var i = elements.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
                var el = elements[i];
                var issueRow = mqIssueRowFromTarget(el);
                if (issueRow) { mqSummaryRemoveRow(mqRowInfo(issueRow)); }
                toRemove.push(fileRowFor(el) || el);
            }
            for (var r = 0; r < toRemove.length; r++) {
                if (toRemove[r].parentNode) { toRemove[r].parentNode.removeChild(toRemove[r]); }
            }
            var sidebarItems = document.querySelectorAll('.sidebar .' + escapedClass);
            sidebarItems.forEach(function(sidebarItem) {
                sidebarItem.parentNode.removeChild(sidebarItem);
            });
            removeEmptyCheckSections();
            mqOnReportMutation({ syncFilters: true, syncNav: true });
        }

        function removeEmptyCheckSections() {
            var checkSections = document.getElementsByClassName('check-section-wrapper');
            for (var i = 0; i < checkSections.length; i++) {
                var checkSectionWrapper = checkSections[i];
                var checkSection = checkSectionWrapper.getElementsByClassName('check-section')[0];
                var fileLists = checkSection.getElementsByClassName('file-list');
                var allHidden = true;
                for (var j = 0; j < fileLists.length; j++) {
                    if (fileLists[j].parentNode) { allHidden = false; break; }
                }
                if (allHidden) {
                    var sidebarItems = document.querySelectorAll('.sidebar .' + checkSectionWrapper.id);
                    sidebarItems.forEach(function (sidebarItem) {
                        sidebarItem.parentNode.removeChild(sidebarItem);
                    });
                    hiddenSections.push(checkSectionWrapper.id);
                    checkSectionWrapper.parentNode.removeChild(checkSectionWrapper);
                    i--;
                }
            }
        }

        function hideCheckSection(id) {
            var wrapper = document.getElementById(id);
            if (wrapper) {
                mqEnsureSummary();
                var rows = wrapper.querySelectorAll('.mq-issue-row');
                for (var i = 0; i < rows.length; i++) {
                    mqSummaryRemoveRow(mqRowInfo(rows[i]));
                }
                wrapper.parentNode.removeChild(wrapper);
                hiddenSections.push(id);
            }
            var sidebarItems = document.querySelectorAll('.sidebar .' + escapeCssSelector(id));
            sidebarItems.forEach(function (sidebarItem) {
                sidebarItem.parentNode.removeChild(sidebarItem);
            });
            mqOnReportMutation({ syncFilters: true, syncNav: true });
        }

        function printReport() { window.print(); }

        function openSaveHelp() {
            var overlay = document.getElementById('save-help-overlay');
            if (overlay) { overlay.classList.add('open'); }
        }

        function closeSaveHelp() {
            var overlay = document.getElementById('save-help-overlay');
            if (overlay) { overlay.classList.remove('open'); }
        }

        function syncViewFilterForSave() {
            var sel = document.getElementById('sidebar-view-filter');
            if (!sel) { return; }
            var mode = sel.value;
            document.body.setAttribute('data-mq-view-filter', mode);
            var options = sel.options;
            for (var i = 0; i < options.length; i++) {
                if (options[i].value === mode) {
                    options[i].setAttribute('selected', 'selected');
                } else {
                    options[i].removeAttribute('selected');
                }
            }
        }

        function restoreViewFilterFromDom() {
            var sel = document.getElementById('sidebar-view-filter');
            if (!sel) { return; }
            var mode = document.body.getAttribute('data-mq-view-filter');
            if (!mode) { return; }
            for (var i = 0; i < sel.options.length; i++) {
                if (sel.options[i].value === mode) {
                    sel.value = mode;
                    return;
                }
            }
        }

        function prepareDocumentForSave() {
            closeSaveHelp();
            syncViewFilterForSave();
            if (scoreViewAdjusted) {
                document.body.setAttribute('data-mq-adjusted', '1');
            }
        }

        function buildReportHtmlForSave() {
            return '<!DOCTYPE html>\n' + document.documentElement.outerHTML;
        }

        function downloadAdjustedReport() {
            var html = buildReportHtmlForSave();
            var blob = new Blob([html], { type: 'text/html;charset=utf-8' });
            var url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
            var link = document.createElement('a');
            link.href = url;
            link.download = 'index.html';
            document.body.appendChild(link);
            link.click();
            document.body.removeChild(link);
            URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
            clearReportSessionDirty();
        }

        function saveAdjustedReport() {
            prepareDocumentForSave();
            if (window.showSaveFilePicker) {
                var html = buildReportHtmlForSave();
                var blob = new Blob([html], { type: 'text/html;charset=utf-8' });
                window.showSaveFilePicker({
                    suggestedName: 'index.html',
                    types: [{ description: 'HTML', accept: { 'text/html': ['.html'] } }]
                }).then(function (handle) {
                    return handle.createWritable().then(function (writable) {
                        return writable.write(blob).then(function () {
                            return writable.close();
                        });
                    });
                }).then(function () {
                    clearReportSessionDirty();
                }).catch(function (err) {
                    if (err && err.name === 'AbortError') { return; }
                    downloadAdjustedReport();
                });
                return;
            }
            downloadAdjustedReport();
        }

        function initBeforeUnloadWarning() {
            window.addEventListener('beforeunload', function (e) {
                if (!reportSessionDirty) { return; }
                e.preventDefault();
                e.returnValue = '';
            });
        }

        (function () {
            function clearSidebarNavActive() {
                var nodes = document.querySelectorAll('.sidebar ul li.sidebar-nav-active');
                for (var i = 0; i < nodes.length; i++) {
                    nodes[i].classList.remove('sidebar-nav-active');
                }
            }
            function setActiveOnLink(a) {
                if (!a) { return; }
                var li = a.closest ? a.closest('li') : null;
                if (!li && a.parentNode && a.parentNode.tagName === 'LI') { li = a.parentNode; }
                if (li) { li.classList.add('sidebar-nav-active'); }
            }
            function setActiveSidebarNavFromHash() {
                clearSidebarNavActive();
                var hash = (window.location.hash || '').trim();
                if (!hash || hash.length < 2) { return; }
                var sb = document.querySelector('.sidebar');
                if (!sb) { return; }
                var links = sb.querySelectorAll('ul a[href^="#"]');
                var link = null;
                for (var j = 0; j < links.length; j++) {
                    if (links[j].getAttribute('href') === hash) { link = links[j]; break; }
                }
                setActiveOnLink(link);
            }
            function initSidebarNavHighlight() {
                var sb = document.querySelector('.sidebar');
                if (!sb) { return; }
                sb.addEventListener('click', function (ev) {
                    var a = ev.target.closest ? ev.target.closest('a') : null;
                    if (!a) { return; }
                    var href = a.getAttribute('href') || '';
                    if (href.charAt(0) !== '#') { return; }
                    clearSidebarNavActive();
                    setActiveOnLink(a);
                });
                window.addEventListener('hashchange', setActiveSidebarNavFromHash);
                setActiveSidebarNavFromHash();
            }
            function initModelThumbDrag() {
                var wraps = document.querySelectorAll('a.model-thumb-wrap[href]');
                for (var i = 0; i < wraps.length; i++) {
                    (function (wrap) {
                        var img = wrap.querySelector('img');
                        if (img) {
                            img.setAttribute('draggable', 'false');
                        }
                        wrap.addEventListener('dragstart', function (e) {
                            var rel = wrap.getAttribute('href');
                            if (!rel) { return; }
                            var fileUrl;
                            try {
                                fileUrl = new URL(rel, window.location.href).href;
                            } catch (err) {
                                fileUrl = rel;
                            }
                            e.dataTransfer.setData('text/uri-list', fileUrl);
                            e.dataTransfer.setData('text/plain', fileUrl);
                            e.dataTransfer.effectAllowed = 'copy';
                        });
                    })(wraps[i]);
                }
            }
            function initSaveHelpDialog() {
                var overlay = document.getElementById('save-help-overlay');
                if (!overlay) { return; }
                overlay.addEventListener('click', function (ev) {
                    if (ev.target === overlay) { closeSaveHelp(); }
                });
                document.addEventListener('keydown', function (ev) {
                    if (ev.key === 'Escape' && overlay.classList.contains('open')) {
                        closeSaveHelp();
                    }
                });
            }
            function initPersistedReportState() {
                if (document.body.getAttribute('data-mq-adjusted') === '1') {
                    scoreViewAdjusted = true;
                    return;
                }
                var titleEl = document.getElementById('mq-page-title');
                if (titleEl && titleEl.textContent.trim() === 'Adjusted Score') {
                    scoreViewAdjusted = true;
                }
            }
            function initReportUi() {
                initPersistedReportState();
                restoreViewFilterFromDom();
                syncFlaggedFilterOptions();
                mqInitSidebarNavOrder();
                mqInitPassBaseline();
                mqInitCategoryCards();
                var baked = document.querySelector('.mq-dashboard[data-mq-summary-baked="1"]');
                var adjusted = document.body.getAttribute('data-mq-adjusted') === '1';
                if (!adjusted) {
                    syncViewFilterOptions();
                }
                initSidebarNavHighlight();
                initHealthCheckJumps();
                initModelJumps();
                initModelThumbDrag();
                initSaveHelpDialog();
                initBeforeUnloadWarning();
                var persistedFilter = document.body.getAttribute('data-mq-view-filter');
                var sel = document.getElementById('sidebar-view-filter');
                var mode = sel ? sel.value : 'all';
                if (persistedFilter || (mode && mode !== 'all')) {
                    applyViewFilter();
                }
                if (adjusted || !baked) {
                    mqRebuildSummaryFromDom();
                    mqApplySummaryToDom();
                } else {
                    var rebuildSummary = function () { mqRebuildSummaryFromDom(); };
                    if (window.requestIdleCallback) {
                        requestIdleCallback(rebuildSummary, { timeout: 2500 });
                    } else {
                        setTimeout(rebuildSummary, 50);
                    }
                    updateSaveButtonVisibility();
                }
            }
            if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
                document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initReportUi);
            } else {
                initReportUi();
            }
        })();
    </script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="sidebar">
    <button class="button print-button" onclick="printReport()">Print This</button>
    <button class="button" type="button" id="save-help-button" style="display: none;" onclick="openSaveHelp()">Save</button>
    <div class="sidebar-filter-wrap" id="sidebar-filter-wrap">
        <label class="sidebar-filter-label" for="sidebar-view-filter">Filter view</label>
        <select id="sidebar-view-filter" class="sidebar-stat-filter" onchange="applyViewFilter()">
            <option value="all" selected>Show all</option>
            <option value="warning">Show warnings</option>
            <option value="error">Show errors</option>
            <option value="flagged">Show flagged</option>
            <option value="unflagged">Show unflagged</option>
            <option value="sort-by-count">Sort by issue count</option>
            <optgroup label="By model" id="sidebar-model-filter-group">
                <option value="PRT">Parts</option>
                <option value="ASM">Assemblies</option>
                <option value="DRW">Drawings</option>
            </optgroup>
            <optgroup label="By category" id="sidebar-category-filter-group">
                <option value="Consistency">Consistency</option>
                <option value="Design Intent Strength">Design Intent Strength</option>
                <option value="Geometry Quality">Geometry Quality</option>
                <option value="Model Complexity">Model Complexity</option>
                <option value="Model Integrity">Model Integrity</option>
                <option value="MBD Readiness">MBD Readiness</option>
            </optgroup>
        </select>
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="#summary">Score</a></li>
        <li><a href="#statistics">Scan Statistics</a></li>
        <hr>
        {% for section in check_sections %}
        <li title="{{ section.category }}" class="sidebar-check-nav wrapper-{{ section.class }}"
            data-mq-section-id="wrapper-{{ section.class }}"
            data-mq-sidebar-stat="{{ 'ERROR' if section.stat_type == 'ERRORS' else 'WARNING' }}"
            data-mq-category="{{ section.category | e }}">
            <a href="#{{ section.class }}">{{ section.name }} ({{ section.count }})</a>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</div>

<a id="summary"></a>
<div class="container main-content">
    <div class="summary">
        <div id="summary-section">
            {{ summary_div }}
            {{ statistics_div }}
        </div>
    </div>

    {% for section in check_sections %}
    <a id="{{ section.class }}"></a>
    <div class="check-section-wrapper" id="wrapper-{{ section.class }}"
         data-mq-section-stat="{{ 'ERROR' if section.stat_type == 'ERRORS' else 'WARNING' }}"
         data-mq-category="{{ section.category | e }}"
         data-mq-check-name="{{ section.model_check_name | e }}">
        <div class="check-header">
            <div class="check-title">
                <h2 id="{{ section.class }}"><span class="bold-text">{{ section.stat_type }}:</span> {{ section.count }} {{ section.name }}</h2>
                <p><strong>Category:</strong> {{ section.category }}</p>
                <p>{{ section.description }}</p>
                <div class="why">{{ section.why | safe }}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="check-buttons">
                <button class="hide-button" onclick="hideCheckSection('wrapper-{{ section.class }}')">Remove&nbsp;this</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="check-section {{ section.class }}" id="{{ section.class }}">
            {% for file in section.files %}
            <div class="file-row">
            <div class="file-list mq-issue-row {{ file.stat }}{{ (file.desc or '').replace(' ', '').replace(':', '\\:').replace('.', '\\.') }}"
                 id="{{ file.file_list_id | escape }}"
                 data-mq-stat="{{ file.stat }}"
                 data-mq-category="{{ file.category | e }}"
                 data-mq-pro-type="{{ file.pro_type | e }}"
                 data-mq-model="{{ file.display_name | e }}">
                {% if file.image_url %}
                    {% if file.model_href %}
                <a class="model-thumb-wrap" href="{{ file.model_href | safe }}" onclick="void(0); return false;">
                    <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" draggable="false" title="Drag this into Creo" src="{{ file.image_url | e }}" alt="" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.style.display='none';"/></a>
                    {% else %}
                <span class="model-thumb-wrap" title="No file link: session-style model name (not used as a file URL).">
                    <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" title="No file link for this model name" src="{{ file.image_url | e }}" alt="" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.style.display='none';"/></span>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endif %}
                <p>{% if file.model_href %}<a href="{{ file.model_href | safe }}" onclick="void(0); return false;">{{ file.display_name_link_text | e }}</a>{% else %}<span class="model-name-plain">{{ file.display_name | e }}</span>{% endif %}&nbsp;
                    {% if file.more_info_link %}
                    <button type="button" onclick="openPopup(event, '{{ file.more_info_link | safe }}');">More details...</button>
                    {% else %}
                    <span class="dimmed-button" title="No matching ModelCHECK detail HTML (*.P.html / *.A.html / *.D.html) found in this folder.">No detail file</span>
                    {% endif %}
                </p>
                <p><strong>{{ file.stat }}:</strong> {{ file.desc | e }}</p>
                <p>{{ file.condensed_msg | e }}</p>
                <p><strong>Created by:</strong> {{ file.last_saved }} on {{ file.created }}</p>
                <p><strong>File Size:</strong> {{ file.file_size }}</p>
                <p><strong>Number of Features:</strong> {{ file.num_features }}</p>
                <p><strong>Model Overall Size:</strong> {{ file.overall_size }}</p>
                <p><strong>Model Units for Length:</strong> {{ file.units_length }}</p>
                <div class="check-buttons">
                    <button class="flag-button button" onclick="toggleFlag('{{ file.file_list_id | escape }}')">Flag&nbsp;this</button>
                    <button class="hide-button button" onclick="hideElementById('{{ file.file_list_id | escape }}')">Remove&nbsp;only&nbsp;this</button>
                    <button class="hide-button button" onclick="hideElementsByClass('{{ file.stat }}{{ (file.desc or '').replace(' ', '').replace(':', '\\:').replace('.', '\\.') }}')">Remove&nbsp;all&nbsp;like&nbsp;this</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="save-help-overlay" id="save-help-overlay" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="save-help-title">
    <div class="save-help-dialog">
        <button class="save-help-close" type="button" aria-label="Close" onclick="closeSaveHelp()">&times;</button>
        <h2 id="save-help-title">Save your adjusted report</h2>
        <p><strong>Ctrl+S</strong> often does not keep flags or other edits on a local report. Use <strong>Save index.html</strong> to write the current page to disk.</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Click <strong>Save index.html</strong>.</li>
            <li>Choose your working folder and replace the existing <strong>index.html</strong>.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>If no save dialog appears, the file downloads to your Downloads folder — move it to the working folder and replace <strong>index.html</strong>.</p>
        <div class="save-help-actions">
            <button class="button" type="button" onclick="saveAdjustedReport()">Save index.html</button>
            <button class="button" type="button" onclick="closeSaveHelp()">Close</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
